<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Rate Sheet Status Update</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
        <h2 style="color: #2b3674; border-bottom: 2px solid #4f9bf5; padding-bottom: 10px;">
            Rate Sheet Status Update
        </h2>
        
        <p>Hello,</p>
        
        <p>The rate sheet <strong>"{{ rate_sheet_name }}"</strong> that you created has been <strong>{{ status }}</strong>.</p>
        
        <div style="background-color: #f8fafd; border-left: 4px solid #4f9bf5; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0;">
            <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>Rate Sheet Details:</strong></p>
            <ul style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                <li><strong>Name:</strong> {{ rate_sheet_name }}</li>
                <li><strong>Status:</strong> {{ status }}</li>
                <li><strong>Effective Date:</strong> {{ effective_date }}</li>
                <li><strong>Reviewed By:</strong> {{ reviewer_email }}</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        {% if reject_comment %}
        <div style="background-color: #fff5f5; border-left: 4px solid #cc1b0c; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0;">
            <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0;"><strong>Rejection Reason:</strong></p>
            <p style="margin: 0; white-space: pre-wrap;">{{ reject_comment }}</p>
        </div>
        {% endif %}
        
        <p>You can view the rate sheet details by visiting the rate sheet management page.</p>
        
        <p style="margin-top: 30px;">
            <a href="{{ rate_sheet_list_url }}" style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #4f9bf5; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold;">
                View Rate Sheets
            </a>
        </p>
        
        <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #e6eaf5; margin: 30px 0;">
        
        <p style="color: #718096; font-size: 12px;">
            This is an automated message from {{ site_name }}. Please do not reply to this email.
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
